HBA Calls for Volunteers - Your Help is Needed  The HBA needs volunteer attorneys to help answer legal questions and provide general guidance to members of the public dealing with the aftermath of recent flooding.
Your help is needed to staff special LegalLine Sessions, to respond to phone calls received through the SBOT/HBA hot line and to provide information at relief centers.
The HBA is accepting volunteers with hours or days to contribute.
Read on for further details about these volunteer opportunities and to learn about training opportunities.
